
'''The Season of Men'''  ni filime y'ikinamico yo mu 2000 [[Ubufaransa|y’Abafaransa]]-[[Tuniziya]] iyobowe na Moufida Tlatli<ref>https://www.trigon-film.org/en/shop/DVD/The_Season_of_Men_-_Maussim_al-riyal</ref> . Yerekanwe mu gice cya Un Certain Regard mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2000<ref>https://www.kviff.com/en/programme/film/44/18241-the-season-of-men</ref> .  Umutwe wa filime, Igihe cy'abagabo, werekeza ukwezi kumwe kwumwaka abagabo  baza ku kirwa cya Djerba<ref>https://www.spiritualityandpractice.com/films/reviews/view/3345</ref>. 

