== Umugambi ==
Umusore w'imyaka 18 ku kirwa cya Djerba, Aïcha, yashakanye na Said, ukora muri Tuniziya igihe kinini cy'umwaka<ref>https://filmsdulosange.com/en/film/the-season-of-men/</ref>. Mbere yuko ashobora kubana na we muri Tuniziya, Said amusaba ko yamuha umuhungu<ref>https://www.istanbulmodern.org/en/cinema/the-season-of-men_2779.html</ref>.  Ku kirwa cya Djerba, Aïcha abaho ategekwa na nyirabukwe, hamwe n'abandi bagore bake, mu gihe abagabo babo bakorera ahandi<ref>https://variety.com/2000/film/reviews/the-season-of-men-1117780961/</ref>. Aïcha yaje kubyara umuhungu kandi yemerewe kwimukira muri Tuniziya hamwe n'umugabo we. Ariko, umuhungu we Aziz afite ibibazo by'ubuzima, bigatuma Saïd amwanga. Aïcha asubira i Djerba, kuri iyi nshuro ari kumwe n'umuhungu we Aziz n'abakobwa be babiri bakuru<ref>https://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2001/06/27/la_saison_des_hommes_2001_review.shtml</ref>. Iyi filime ikoresha ibintu byinshi byagaragaye hagati ya Aïcha n’abakobwa be bato batuye i Djerba mbere y’ivuka rya Aziz hanyuma igaragara muri iki gihe, aho Aziz afite imyaka umunani, mbere yuko asubira i Djerba<ref>https://www.nytimes.com/2001/09/28/movies/film-review-married-but-seldom-with-a-husband.html</ref>. Filime irangira Aïcha na Aziz bakorana bombi bakora imyenda, bakora kaseti Aïcha agurisha. Filime irangira umukobwa muto wa Aïcha Emna agenda, Aïcha na Aziz babana i Djerba<ref>https://podiumaudio.com/book-series/seasons-of-man/</ref>.

